version_description:
• A new look and improved stability for Deposit Checks
• Optimizations that make Ent Mobile faster

Optimized for iOS 8
Improved stability of Deposit Checks

Camera privacy updates for Deposit Checks feature
Location finder updates

• Improved check deposit image capture experience
• Touch ID authentication for iOS 9 devices
• Updated splash screens that match the new theme
• Improved performance
• Minor bug fixes and improvements

With the latest app release you can:
• Get available account balances and last five transactions with just a tap
• View account details including dividends, rate, payment date, and interest accrual
• Update your contact information, reset your password, or change your username
• Transfer funds between Ent accounts
• Set up new billers and add payment reminders
• Change your certificate maturity and dividend options
• Control access to your account by creating new users and setting permissions
• Administer your account by adding overdraft protection or ordering checks
• Download account information to spreadsheet, Quicken, and more

Now supporting business accounts!
Manage your business accounts from your phone or tablet, when it’s convenient for you.
• Send a wire
• Schedule one-time and recurring ACH transactions
• Have full control over what your users can see and do on your account
• Monitor account activity
• Quickly and securely toggle between accounts with Switch Accounts

Touch ID is a trademark of Apple Inc.

•Bug fix for some older iOS devices that were blocking mobile deposit
•General enhancements and improvements

•General enhancements and improvements
•Updates to support iOS 10
Enhancements and improvements to remote deposit

• Automatic check image capture
• Enhanced check images
• View check deposit history
• View pending deposits
• Other enhancements and improvements
This update includes a fix for broken telephone links
